OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with band
OL,6,Fof rain spreading eastwards, perhaps
OL,7,Fwith the odd heavier burst. Rain
OL,8,Fclearing east by midday, leaving sunny
OL,9,Fspells with isolated showers
OL,10,Fdeveloping, perhaps heavy in western
OL,11,Fparts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA breezy night with most
OL,14,Fareas remaining dry with clear spells
OL,15,Flikely across the region. Southern
OL,16,Fareas will see risk of blustery
OL,17,Fshowers, especially near coasts.
OL,18,FChilly inland by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
