OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSome sunshine for Sunday but
OL,6,Fincreasingly showery with some
OL,7,Fbecoming heavy by afternoon brining a
OL,8,Frisk of thunder. A windy day with
OL,9,Ftemperatures mostly near average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FSunshine and showers for Monday, with
OL,13,Fheavy downpours again. Drier by
OL,14,Fevening. Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,15,Fcloudier with increasing chance of
OL,16,Fshowery rain. Breezy, but milder with
OL,17,Fslightly above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
